@iNetwork wrote:

[B][CENTER]Here’s a re-release of Hybris

What have i done… Iv added Gnome agility, Fixed alot of bugs & dupes
Also fixed all previous errors

Other things, Working Compiler, Download Have Fun

Hybris.zip
[/CENTER]

24pz709.png978×356

[center]
Download Client

[/center]

6g8le9.png712×950

~ Hybris Features ~

Server Stability:

Region clipping for both npcs and players. Absolutely no lag.
Uses cycle event manager for 90% of event processing.
Can hold up to 500+ Players without lag, has been tested.
Uses mina networking, added few packets to process immediately.

Quests

7 fully working quests.
All have quest interfaces and are managed in separation(npc clicking, button clicking, object clicking)
Correct interfaces for rewards.
All have rewards.

Minigames:

Fully working duel arena, all major bugs fixed.
Fully working barrows with reward chest.
Working fight pits and fight caves.
Very basic form of Castle wars.
Fully working king black dragon transportation using canoes at Lumbridge(Waka canoe)

Skills:

Fully working mining with correct pickaxe animations, delays and empty rock.
Fully working woodcutting with correct animations of axes, delays, stumps.
Fully working herblore with correct herb identifying and potion creation.
Fully working firemaking using clipping via region manager with fires and ashes.
Fully working thieving, handled completely from scratch. Stalls empty and respawn with delays.
Started very basic base of runecrafting.
Mining pure essence at level 30 automatically handled with timers!
Fully working fishing with different types of fish caught at different levels. All types of fishing are handled.
Very basic base of smithing added, making bars and smithing into armour handled through interfaces.
Slayer base added.
Fully working fletching.
Fully working crafting with perfect handled gem timers.

Misc features:

Fully working flax spinning into bow strings handled.
Fully working fountain filling system.
Fully working amulet of glory degrading.
Fully working dueling ring with degrading.
Added a significant amount of shops in all of the cities properly with dialogues!
Working teletab transportation.
Working ship sailing transportation.
Basic rug travel methods.
Rock crab travel at Camelot.
Re-did food eating management.
Other forms of transportation includes gates, doors, double doors and magic teleporting with level requirements and runes.

PVP/COMBAT

Fully working mage, range, attack timers.
All basic spells working, ancients working, in player panel you can find Vengeance which works both on players and npcs.
PVP shop automatic updating for every kill you make.
PVP kill point system activated in wilderness.
Multi zones working correctly.
Fixed all correct arrow backs for range weapons such as Crystal bow.

NPCS

Fully clipped walking!
Fully clipping following player while attacking.
Working various types of npcs (Mage,Range,Melee,Hybrids)
Several npc drops.
Traverley accessible at Barb village with all the npcs added in correct spots with their individual drops.
Dragon fireshield method added for both npcs and players.
